A Zimbabwean woman was on Saturday send in ICU after what seemed to be a romantic day with a married man went wrong.According to Zimbabwean sources, the woman was mauled by two lions during an attempt to take a selfie closer to their deadly jaws.The Harare Police spokesperson Assistant Commissioner Charity Charamba confirmed the incident, and urged the game park visitors to consider safety first before anything else. She therefore reveals that the police are doing their level best to ensure tourists are educated about the dangers of wild animals.The condition of the woman is unknown..To view the Pics click next..[ WARNING GRAPHIC IMAGES]&nbsp;